Class Product

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.warehouse.Product
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Product>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Order
public class Product extends Object implements Comparable<Product>
The Product class defines a product object:

An instance of Product contains all the data that identifies the product itself, you can compare two products, and get or set any of it's attributes

To manage lists or maps of products refer to
